{"tid":308372,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問巴士迷係咪都好憎的士同地鐵？","createTime":"2017-07-04T06:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T02:08:21.000Z","uid":19657,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"251c079f807c32f7cfe775512a9edd74c6b06fd8","tid":308372,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"我對巴士迷冇惡意，興趣一種，研究下車種同路線嗰啲咁...<br />\n<br />\n但我有個ＦＤ成日都話好想的士同港鐵消失，咁九巴就可以增加路線同班次，全香港可以一齊搭巴士。起初我以為佢係鳩ＵＰ，後來先知佢係認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我問佢，香港係得咁多馬路，依家收工已經日日塞車，你仲要全世界同你搭巴士，塞到幾時先返到屋企？佢話叫我唔好干涉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢識嗰啲巴迷個個都係咁諗<br />\n<br />\n我真心想知佢啲巴迷朋友邊到識返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇連登巴迷可以解答下我"},{"pid":"916147d916ee5f58cdb95d365c7585ced133f69d","tid":308372,"uid":98680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"當你沉迷結衣既時候<br />\n就會覺得長澤正美唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實兩個都咁撚正"},{"pid":"1df985e4c7b5ebf13e567c841f8b849a1d9458a7","tid":308372,"uid":25460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"呢度有個巴膠post 歡迎你入去問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362d77d3749f1794226dba473cfbba59a723a1af","tid":308372,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你沉迷結衣既時候<br />\n就會覺得長澤正美唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實兩個都咁撚正</blockquote><br />\n但佢點解唔會理性思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個大城市點可能只依靠一種公共交通工具"},{"pid":"47ef046d7d2b693c6c07b499c2cfcd40083715e7","tid":308372,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度有個巴膠post 歡迎你入去問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地有人地討論，我插埋去問呢Ｄ無聊野好無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b69045257bd12e630b0acd02e618f0a58143bfb","tid":308372,"uid":88493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"你朋友應該唔係巴迷而係智障"},{"pid":"c41298effa5a8ebf3fa6301c9302d18f1d3eeeb8","tid":308372,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"唔係巴迷，唔會研究巴士車種，唔會記巴士車牌，但好鍾意搭巴士，覺得搭地鐵只適宜搭兩、三個站😂"},{"pid":"400b9db600a8a7ec29142b0d9e2c2d35e881efa5","tid":308372,"uid":25460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度有個巴膠post 歡迎你入去問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地有人地討論，我插埋去問呢Ｄ無聊野好無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇話無唔無聊嘅 起碼唔離題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6e68b9d86429b79964c571e53b16f9f1d26f44","tid":308372,"uid":35507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"香港政府偏幫地鐵又真係抵屌既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a8cdfe8266ff28c04cc61783436f12f11f3aac","tid":308372,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"地鐵無死氣喉俾佢屌"},{"pid":"89921397d3205b8414c4d77e2716dbc24d89f356","tid":308372,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"佢鍾意FF下姐"},{"pid":"e16c6017fd0dcbcef0eda45f6c999e4bd2d0b851","tid":308372,"uid":17759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇樣就知你朋友係鍾意巴士 鍾意到毒到出煙嘅地步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要成個世界圍住個巴士轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ac99acb67996f5e05677e87e8a6a3ed60766b7","tid":308372,"uid":26506,"like":0,"